verses.name: Judges 1:29
verses.text: Neither did Ephraim drive out the Canaanites that dwelt in Gezer; but the Canaanites dwelt in Gezer among them.

verses.name: Judges 1:30
verses.text: Neither did Zebulun drive out the inhabitants of Kitron, nor the inhabitants of Nahalol; but the Canaanites dwelt among them, and became tributaries.

verses.name: Judges 1:31
verses.text: Neither did Asher drive out the inhabitants of Accho, nor the inhabitants of Zidon, nor of Ahlab, nor of Achzib, nor of Helbah, nor of Aphik, nor of Rehob:

verses.name: Judges 1:32
verses.text: But the Asherites dwelt among the Canaanites, the inhabitants of the land: for they did not drive them out.
